import math

n = int(input())
min_n = n
min_op = 0

while n > 1:
    if n % 2 == 0:
        n = n // 2
        min_op += 1
    else:
        n = math.sqrt(n)
        min_op += 1
    if n < min_n:
        min_n = n

print(min_n, min_op)
